locality: Tampoketsa d'Ankazobe. Forested region along RN4, near the village of Manankazo, and the river of the same name. Embankment on road, 50 m S of bridge at R. Manankazo.
Dct Ankazobe, CR Fihaonana, Fkt Andranovelona, Inselberg de Lohavohitra, PK 45 de la RN 4 allant d'Antananarivo - Mahajanga, sur le côté droit. Séchage direct.
Ankazobe, 112 km d'Antananarivo sur la route RN 4 sur cuirasse ferrallitique.
